; Coverage test for times.cc lines 740-742
; Exercise "N quarters ago/hence" expressions
; These exercise the QUARTERS arithmetic (amount * 3 * adjust)

2020/01/01 Old
    Expenses:Food            $10.00
    Assets:Cash

; "2 quarters ago" exercises QUARTERS + AGO path
test reg Expenses --begin "2 quarters ago"
end test

; "1 quarters hence" exercises QUARTERS + HENCE path
test reg Expenses --begin "1 quarters hence"
end test
